game.ui

Class Locations

  • java.lang.Object
    • game.ui.Locations

  • public class Locations
extends Object
    Stores all the locations of the objects that are drawn on the screen. Makes it easier to change them and use them in different actions.
    Author:
    Eero Kuurne
